 to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tilted map."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"id